your daughter.

90
00:05:16,577 --> 00:05:18,448
- That's Madison.

91
00:05:18,622 --> 00:05:22,409
- Well, you look just like
your mother.

92
00:05:22,583 --> 00:05:24,019
What's the matter
with your nose?

93
00:05:24,193 --> 00:05:26,021
- [Laughs]

94
00:05:26,195 --> 00:05:27,414
Kids. You know how it is.

95
