to our sleepy little town.

101
00:05:40,427 --> 00:05:42,777
- Hmm.
- We're building a mall.

102
00:05:42,951 --> 00:05:45,301
Who'd have thunk it?

103
00:05:45,475 --> 00:05:47,651
And after the mall, we're going
to get ourselves a casino,

104
00:05:47,825 --> 00:05:49,479
condos, golf courses.

105
00:05:49,653 --> 00:05:51,655
Yes, sir. The new hope.
- Sounds great, Arliss.

106
00:05:51,829 --> 00:05:54,789
- Bobby, Bobby, Bobby.
- Bobby?

107
00:05:54,963 --> 00:05:57,792
- Well, we've called him that
since he's been about that high.

108
00:05:57,966 --> 00:06:01,012
I'll tell ya, I was a good buddy
of your grandpa's.

109
00:06:01,186 --> 00:06:03,667
May he rest in peace.

110
00:06:03,841 --> 00:06:05,800
Ooh, you got something there
on your nose.

111
00:06:05,974 --> 00:06:08,106
Here, uh, here.

112
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:10,718
Go ahead, you can keep it.

113
