No crime here.
[Laughs]

115
00:06:16,071 --> 00:06:18,682
So, if you want to back out of
this, we'll understand.

116
00:06:18,856 --> 00:06:20,510
- Oh, I'm here, Arliss.

117
00:06:20,684 --> 00:06:22,077
I might as well do the job
'til the next election.

118
00:06:22,251 --> 00:06:27,299
- Well, then ok.
Welcome.

119
00:06:27,474 --> 00:06:31,434
Probably, well, just like
you remember it right Bobby?

120
00:06:31,608 --> 00:06:33,044
- Yep.

