00:06:38,093 --> 00:06:41,792
- Bobby. You look so much
like him.

125
00:06:41,966 --> 00:06:44,491
[Laughs]

126
00:06:44,665 --> 00:06:47,319
- My daughter Madison.
- Hello.

127
00:06:47,494 --> 00:06:49,539
- Your pa's secretary
for so long,

128
00:06:49,713 --> 00:06:51,323
people can't even remember
when she started.

129
00:06:51,498 --> 00:06:53,543
