Good for you.

130
00:06:53,717 --> 00:06:55,327
I tell you,
isn't life funny, huh?

131
00:06:55,502 --> 00:06:56,764
Huh? [Laughs]

132
00:06:56,938 --> 00:06:58,635
You know what this
reminds me of?

133
00:06:58,809 --> 00:07:00,115
